recipesJson.name: Raven's Early Autumn Orchard V2
recipesJson.author: DrkRaven1
recipesJson.description:
Inspiration; Spring has come and gone, the bees pollinated all the trees and and the heat of summer has given way. The trees are now bearing fruit. It's time to pick and enjoy the juice. Mix it up and fill your tank or drip to your hearts content.

Allow a friend to try the blend and as the Apples and Peach prevail a note of... Can they figure it out? 

DIY-eJuice on Discord Join for all the assistance you need
